executionArgs.additionalInstruction: Re-running backend tests after code fixes. The following fixes have been applied: 1) API response formats fixed (visit types and consult types return arrays, patient returns fields at root level), 2) Field name flexibility (accepts both camelCase and snake_case), 3) Middleware enhanced to check cookies for admin API routes, 4) Error messages improved. Please test all endpoints again and verify if the fixes resolved the issues. Note: Database seeding may still be needed for some tests.
